{"id": "1489857696281788476", "channel_id": "1489857696281788476", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "Keeper\n  Due to some technical anomalies, Keepers who installed the client after 4:30 PM(UTC+8) on April 3rd, or who have performed a client repair, may experience an issue where the in-game language still displays in Chinese despite the language setting being set to \"English.\" Our staff are currently working on an emergency fix for this issue and expect to have it resolved within today. We sincerely apologize for the inconvenience this has caused. Please be patient, Keepers! After the issue is resolved, we will distribute \"Silver\" ×500 as compensation to express our apologies", "timestamp": "2026-04-04T05:22:35.011000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-04T05:52:49.248000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "sorel_wink", "emoji_id": "1468258265656856582", "count": 7}, {"emoji": "🥲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🥳", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1489857696424263700", "filename": "lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 91486, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1489857696281788476/1489857696424263700/lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg?ex=69d1f19b&is=69d0a01b&hm=c4bdc7310c7fc17ef7e0204eb8e46c6857e80d836c14934ae46ead1c471a1c5f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1489857696281788476", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "English Language Setting Abnormality Issue Notice", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
